  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The proposed project will be a multi-centre, prospective observational study to determine the
      prognosis and determinants of functional outcomes of patients with proximal humerus
      fractures. Approximately 10 centres will participate in this observational cohort, each
      enrolling at least 50 patients over the course of 2 years.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
