    <measure>Disabilities of the Arm, Shoulder, and Hand (DASH)</measure>
    <time_frame>2 years</time_frame>
    <description>The DASH is a 30-item, self-report questionnaire designed to measure physical function and symptoms in people with musculoskeletal disorders of the upper limb.</description>
  </primary_outcome>
